"Change Set:		8049CollectionsTests-ar.104CollectionsTests-ar.104:Provides test for UTF8 conversion issue described inhttp://lists.squeakland.org/pipermail/etoys-dev/2009-October/004045.html "!!StringTest methodsFor: 'tests - converting' stamp: 'ar 10/23/2009 09:55'!testUtf8ToSqueakLeadingChar	"Ensure utf8ToSqueak inserts the leading char just like UTF8TextConverter does"	| data |	data := #(227 129 130 227 129 132 227 129 134 227 129 136 227 129 138) asByteArray "aiueo in Japanese".	self assert: data asString utf8ToSqueak = (data asString convertFromEncoding:#utf8)! !